languages.text: "Как я и говорила, шакалы Фалько патрулируют каждую дыру в этом проклятом ажи месте. Вон, видите тех ублюдков? Нужно обойти их, не привлекая внимания, иначе все усилия покатятся к Трону!"

traits.locale_text: "Как я и говорила, шакалы Фалько патрулируют каждую дыру в этом проклятом ажами месте. Вон, видите тех ублюдков? Нужно обойти их, не привлекая внимания, иначе все усилия покатятся к Трону!"
traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: "As I said before, Falco's jackals are patrolling every nook and cranny of this azhi-cursed place. See those scumbags over there? We need to avoid them and not draw any attention to ourselves, or else we might as well dump a pile of grox shit all over our plan!"

languages.text: 「前にも言ったように、ファルコのジャッカルがこのアジーに呪われた場所の隅々まで巡回しているの。あそこにいるクズたちが見えるかしら？あいつらを避けて、注意を引かないようにしなければならないの。さもなければあたしたちの計画に蜥蜴牛のクソを練りこむも同然だ！」

traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: “就像我之前说的，法尔科的那群豺狼正在到处巡逻。他们不会放过这个烂地方的任何角落。看到那群人渣了吗？我们得避开他们，不能引起他们的注意，否则我们的计划就会被搞得稀烂，像格洛克斯兽的屎一样烂！”
languages.original_text: "As I said before, Falco's jackals are patrolling every nook and cranny of this azhi-cursed place. See those scumbags over there? We need to avoid them and not draw any attention to ourselves, or else we might as well dump a pile of grox shit all over our plan!"

traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: «Como dije antes, los esbirros de Falco no dejan rincón de este sitio infestado de azhi sin peinar. ¿Ve a esos capullos de allí? Hay que evitarlos y procurar que no se fijen en nosotros. De lo contrario, ¡estaríamos de mierda de grox hasta el cuello!».
languages.original_text: "As I said before, Falco's jackals are patrolling every nook and cranny of this azhi-cursed place. See those scumbags over there? We need to avoid them and not draw any attention to ourselves, or else we might as well dump a pile of grox shit all over our plan!"

traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: « Comme je vous le disais plus tôt, les larbins de Falco patrouillent dans les moindres recoins de ces satanés tréfonds. Vous voyez ces petits salauds ? Il faut à tout prix éviter d'attirer leur attention. Pas question de ruiner nos plans en se comportant comme un grox dans un magasin de porcelaine ! »
languages.original_text: "As I said before, Falco's jackals are patrolling every nook and cranny of this azhi-cursed place. See those scumbags over there? We need to avoid them and not draw any attention to ourselves, or else we might as well dump a pile of grox shit all over our plan!"

Il faut à tout prix éviter d'attirer leur attention. Pas question de ruiner nos plans en se comportant comme un grox dans un magasin de porcelaine ! »
traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: "Wie schon gesagt, patrouillieren Falcos Schakale durch alle Ecken und Nischen dieses Azhi-verseuchten Orts. Seht Ihr den Abschaum da drüben? Wir sollten ihm ausweichen und keine Aufmerksamkeit erregen, sonst können wir genauso gut einen Haufen Grox-Scheiße über unseren Plan kippen!"
languages.original_text: "As I said before, Falco's jackals are patrolling every nook and cranny of this azhi-cursed place. See those scumbags over there? We need to avoid them and not draw any attention to ourselves, or else we might as well dump a pile of grox shit all over our plan!"

languages.text: "Dediğim gibi Falco'nun çakalları, bu azhi kaynayan yerin her köşesinde kol geziyor. Şuradaki alçakları görüyor musun? Onlardan kaçınmalı, dikkatleri üzerimize çekmemeliyiz. Yoksa planımız komple güme gider!"
languages.original_text: "As I said before, Falco's jackals are patrolling every nook and cranny of this azhi-cursed place. See those scumbags over there? We need to avoid them and not draw any attention to ourselves, or else we might as well dump a pile of grox shit all over our plan!"

traits.locale_text: "Dediğim gibi Falco'nun çakalları, bu azhi kaynayan yerin her köşesinde kol gezmekte. Şuradaki alçakları görüyor musun? Onlara yanaşmamalı, kendimize dikkat çekmemeliyiz. Yoksa planımız komple güme gider!"
traits.speaker: JaeCompanion
